Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数据类型两大类","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211763-8hmy92j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220618211763-8hmy92j","updated":"20220618211763"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/数据类型-20220618215622-n1et9hm.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220618211764-t964clw","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220618211764-t964clw","updated":"20220618211764"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220618211765-7dqy7jd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220618211765-7dqy7jd","updated":"20220618211765"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"long类型要在数字后面加个L        long num=30L;","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211766-z256qa2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220618211766-z256qa2","updated":"20220618211766"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"字符串用String表示，String是类，不是关键字    String name=“钢铁侠”;","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220618211767-iyf5bey","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220618211767-iyf5bey","updated":"20220618211767"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"尽量避免用浮点数进行比较，因为它是有限的，最后会趋于离散\n\n比如   float  A = 213124235434534f；\n\n​\t  float  B = A+1；\n\n​     System.out.println.(A==B);\n\n结果是true 但显然结果应该是false\n如果要精确比较数字可以用java写好的类，BigDecimal\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211768-p379ift","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20220618211768-p379ift","updated":"20220618211768"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"强制类型转转","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211769-rh0abg2","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220618211769-rh0abg2","updated":"20220618211769"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int i = 128;\nbyte b = (byte)i;\n在数前加上（）并写入要转换的类型，这就是强制转换\n\nSystem.out.println(i);\nSystem.out.println(b);//内存溢出\n如果输出上面两个数会发现结果是128和-128，为什么会是负的呢？因为byte的大小是127，给它赋值128就是会导致内存溢出\n\nint i = 128;\ndouble b = i;\n输出分别是128，128.0\n所以     强制转换的使用要求是:     （类型）变量名    变量内存大小——高到低\n         自动转换的使用要求:\t\t\t\t\t\t变量内存大小——低到高\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211770-6a48vqo","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220618211770-6a48vqo","updated":"20220618211770"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"数字之间可以用下划线进行分割\nint money = 10_0000_0000;\nint years = 20;\nint total = money*years;//结果是-1474836480,计算的时候溢出了\nlong total2 = money*years;//结果还是-1474836480，显然运算之前已经默认是int,转换之前已经存在问题了\n\nlong total3 = money*((long)years);//结果是2000000000,在运算的时候就把他的类型进行转换\n\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211771-7k0ot33","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220618211771-7k0ot33","updated":"20220618211771"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"变量","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211772-m7kyg2z","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20220618211772-m7kyg2z","updated":"20220618211772"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实例变量","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211773-5fb88sd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220618211773-5fb88sd","updated":"20220618211773"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/变量类型-20220618215622-ivemrq2.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220618211774-ldumi07","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20220618211774-ldumi07","updated":"20220618211774"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类变量","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211775-go09lva","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220618211775-go09lva","updated":"20220618211775"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{