":"一个类即使什么都不写，它也会存在一个方法","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220618211909-acnqbxe","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220618211909-acnqbxe","updated":"20220618211909"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"构造器：\n1.和类名相同\n2.没有返回值\n\n作用：\n1.new本质在调用构造方法\n2.初始化对象的值\n\n注意点：\n1.定义有参构造之后，无参构造必须显示定义，即把无参构造里面空着\n\n//类\nPublic class Person{\n\tString name;\n\tpublic Person(){} //无参构造必须空着\n\tpublic Person(){ //有参构造\n\t\tthis.name  =  name;\n   }\n}\n\n2.上面代码提到的this. 一般是参数传进来的值\n\n有参构造快捷方式\nAlt + Insert\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211910-74mz3gg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220618211910-74mz3gg","updated":"20220618211910"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"封装","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618211911-xsjxysb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220618211911-xsjxysb","updated":"20220618211911"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/封装-20220618215622-yv4lc9t.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220618220256-t2tojh0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220618220256-t2tojh0","updated":"20220618220312"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"私有.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"